  "title": "Chinese Kindergarten Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Foster social interactions among children to enhance their self-esteem.</li>\n  <li>Utilize creative learning methods, including arts and crafts, supervised play, and storytelling.</li>\n  <li>Develop comprehensive curriculum tailored to early childhood development needs.</li>\n  <li>Promote a sense of order and discipline within the classroom.</li>\n  <li>Supervise children during free time on the playground.</li>\n  <li>Maintain a clean, safe, and organised classroom environment.</li>\n  <li>Prepare for lessons by gathering materials and setting up workstations.</li>\n  <li>Communicate regularly with parents about their child's progress and activities.</li>\n  <li>Compile and prepare children portfolios.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Education, with a focus on Early Childhood Development.</li>\n  <li>Experience working with young children in a classroom setting.</li>\n  <li>Ability to engage with children at their level effectively.</li>\n  <li>Patient and compassionate demeanor, coupled with a friendly, energetic attitude.</li>\n  <li>Creative mindset with the ability to design memorable, innovative lessons.</li>\n  <li>Passion for shaping and inspiring young minds.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with Microsoft Office.</li>\n  <li>Ability to serve as a positive role model.</li>\n</ul>",
